name: Pongs Squad - King Lizard
description:
Pongs Squad is a group of criminals from an unknown country. They are scattered in various parts of the world due to a dispute between their captain and vice-captain.

Kwang Lee Sar is the assassin of this group. He was nicknamed King Lizard. Previously, he was a cat who was very disliked by his master so that his master had the heart to poison him with a dangerous substance and turn almost his entire body into a very strange form. His skin turned into lizard skin and his eyes fused together. Currently, he is hiding somewhere in South Korea.
